data.description: Beautiful home tucked off the road, situated on more than a half acre, in the highly desirable Rehobeth school zone. As you enter you are greeted by wood flooring and a unique doubled sided glass fireplace that welcomes you into the open family room with cathedral ceilings, filled with lovely natural light. To the right are two guest bedrooms, one at each end of the hallway & a nice size guest bathroom in between. To the left is the dining area of this large eat in kitchen where wood floors continue along with plenty of cabinets, a separate pantry, lots of counter space for cooking & ample bar top seating for entertaining guests. Down a short hall is your main suite with cathedral ceilings, large walk in closet & private bathroom oasis including jetted Jacuzzi tub, separate shower for two, dual vanities and linen closet. Laundry room is conveniently located between the kitchen and main suite with additional storage cabinets. From the kitchen, a glass door leads out to your generous  covered back porch overlooking the spacious backyard completely fenced with low maintenance private vinyl fencing. Large attached dry storage room has lots of shelving & space for additional appliances. Also in the backyard a 10x14 semi finished "she shed/man cave" heated & cooled with front porch! Large storage shed for lawn mower & tools. Home & 10x14 building covered under a termite bond. HVAC system serviced semi annually. Security system remains. Impeccably maintained home is move in ready.
